ited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 111, "created": 1773692360000, "id": "2033639271366578665", "video": {"preview": "https://pbs.twimg.com/amplify_video_thumb/2033639218891665408/img/pEzJZ0zoLdy6FNBl.jpg", "mpeg": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2033639218891665408/pl/_YttqvV2nzAQQMO-.m3u8?v=cef", "aspectRatio": [16, 9], "heightRatio": 56, "type": "video/mp4", "url": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2033639218891665408/vid/avc1/480x270/kvR_3yM5sDG-c9V8.mp4"}, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2013475077619359745/SfN8KfMj_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Nick Sortor", "username": "nicksortor"}, "content": "\ud83d\udea8 BREAKING: Stephen Miller says we could BALANCE the national budget if fraud committed by illegal aliens was cut off\n\n\u201cThe extraction of wealth from American taxpayers to people who don't belong here is the PRIMARY CAUSE of the national debt!\u201d \u2014@StephenM\n\nAbsolutely SPOT ON! \ud83d\udd25", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 3614}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASGIwiZdx", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 168, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8493819, "raw_content": "", "author": "Cole_Burns", "created": 1773725588433, "profile_picture": "Ud9D0jYxAxyv", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "45fan", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.patriots.win", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASGIwiZdx.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.patriots.win/post/RgRPmTNgejL6.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/IdCaguUvloRrfhJX.png", "width": 598, "content-type": "png", "height": 468}], "blurhash": "U9FY}z4T0000AhxB-mxt00%MaK%MmP-=p0IV", "full_resolution": [468, 598]}, "title": "\"Sunbathers\" Newest Media Code Word For Non-White Usual Suspects", "last_comment_created": 1773758322628, "content": "", "score_down": 1, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 12, "score_up": 169, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASGIxpb7K", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 35, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8494342, "raw_content": "The Incomprehensible power of the Love of God in Christ Jesus\r\n\r\n\u201cFor I am persuaded, that neither death, nor life, nor angels, nor principalities, nor powers, nor things present, nor things to come, 39 Nor height, nor depth, nor any other creature, shall be able to separate us from the love of God, which is in Christ Jesus our Lord.\u201d (Romans 8:38-39)\r\n\r\nThe love of God is proven in Christ Jesus our Lord. 1 John 4:8 says: \u201cGod is love.\u201d 1 John 4:9 adds: \u201cIn this the love of God was made manifest among us, that God sent his only Son into the world, so that we might live through him.\u201d  You do not know the love of God if you are not in Christ Jesus.  If you are in Christ Jesus, you are the beneficiary of inseparable love because he is Lord. When I grew up in church, the saints would say and sing, \u201cI will let nothing separate me from the love of Christ.\u201d The truth is, we do it all the time. But the love of Jesus will not let you go.\r\n\r\nThis reveals the Perfection of God\u2019s Love. Verse 35 dismisses seven threats to Christ\u2019s love for us. Verse 39 adds ten threats to the list and declares God to be Lord over them all. \r\n\r\nOur Lord Jesus is Lord over everything that exists on Earth or in the Heavens: \u201cDeath nor life.\u201d The finality of \u201cDeath\u201d and the vicissitudes (look up the definition, it will expand your gratefulness of your salvation) of \u201clife\u201d cannot separate us from God\u2019s love. Lord over Spirits:  Angels nor rulers. Heaven\u2019s angels and Satan\u2019s rulers cannot separate you from God\u2019s love. Lord over Time: \u201cThings present nor things to come.\u201d Nothing that happens today or tomorrow can separate you from God\u2019s love. Lord over Powers. No human or spiritual \u201cpowers\u201d can separate us from God\u2019s love. Lord over Space: \u201cnor height nor depth.\u201d Nothing above or under the earth can separate you from God\u2019s love.\r\n", "author": "Come-mistertallyman", "created": 1773756256780, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "usernamenottaken", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "The Incomprehensible power of the Love of God in Christ Jesus", "last_comment_created": 1773757736712, "content": "<p>The Incomprehensible power of the Love of God in Christ Jesus</p>\n<p>\u201cFor I am persuaded, that neither death, nor life, nor angels, nor principalities, nor powers, nor things present, nor things to come, 39 Nor height, nor depth, nor any other creature, shall be able to separate us from the love of God, which is in Christ Jesus our Lord.\u201d (Romans 8:38-39)</p>\n<p>The love of God is proven in Christ Jesus our Lord. 1 John 4:8 says: \u201cGod is love.\u201d 1 John 4:9 adds: \u201cIn this the love of God was made manifest among us, that God sent his only Son into the world, so that we might live through him.\u201d  You do not know the love of God if you are not in Christ Jesus.  If you are in Christ Jesus, you are the beneficiary of inseparable love because he is Lord. When I grew up in church, the saints would say and sing, \u201cI will let nothing separate me from the love of Christ.\u201d The truth is, we do it all the time. But the love of Jesus will not let you go.</p>\n<p>This reveals the Perfection of God\u2019s Love. Verse 35 dismisses seven threats to Christ\u2019s love for us. Verse 39 adds ten threats to the list and declares God to be Lord over them all.</p>\n<p>Our Lord Jesus is Lord over everything that exists on Earth or in the Heavens: \u201cDeath nor life.\u201d The finality of \u201cDeath\u201d and the vicissitudes (look up the definition, it will expand your gratefulness of your salvation) of \u201clife\u201d cannot separate us from God\u2019s love. Lord over Spirits:  Angels nor rulers. Heaven\u2019s angels and Satan\u2019s rulers cannot separate you from God\u2019s love. Lord over Time: \u201cThings present nor things to come.\u201d Nothing that happens today or tomorrow can separate you from God\u2019s love. Lord over Powers. No human or spiritual \u201cpowers\u201d can separate us from God\u2019s love. Lord over Space: \u201cnor height nor depth.\u201d Nothing above or under the earth can separate you from God\u2019s love.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 35, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2033904301173600435", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASGIxq9Pm", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 25, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8494572, "raw_content": "", "author": "rdvs34283", "created"